ou are contracting with\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"These terms govern your use of kvrn.com and any purchase you make from KVRN, operated by [KVRN Ltd], registered in England and Wales (Company No. [XXXXXXXX]). By placing an order, you agree to these terms.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rule\"}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\",\"children\":\"Orders and contract formation\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-3\",\"children\":\"Placing an order is an offer to buy. A contract between you and KVRN is formed when we confirm your order by email — not at the point of placing it.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We reserve the right to cancel any order before dispatch. If we cancel your order, we will refund you in full within 5 business days. We will notify you by email.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rule\"}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\",\"children\":\"Pricing and payment\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"All prices are displayed in GBP and include UK VAT at 20%.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"International orders may be subject to import duties and taxes payable by you.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"We accept payment via Stripe (card, Apple Pay, Google Pay).\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Payment is taken immediately on order confirmation.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"If a pricing error occurs, we will notify you and give you the option to reorder at the correct price or cancel.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rule\"}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\",\"children\":\"Delivery\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-3\",\"children\":\"Delivery times